        <mxCell id="caption" parent="1" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=#555555;fillColor=#f9f9f9;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=9;fontColor=#000000;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=4;" value="&lt;b&gt;Processes:&lt;/b&gt; 1.0 Sensor Data Acquisition · 2.0 Signal Processing &amp; Feature Extraction · 3.1 Rule-Based Analysis · 3.2 ML Analysis (1D CNN) · 4.0 Event Validation · 5.0 Eco Scoring &amp; Fuel Estimation · 6.0 Evidence Capture · 7.0 Live UI Update · 8.0 Trip Persistence · 9.0 Trip History Display&#xa;&lt;b&gt;Data Stores:&lt;/b&gt; D1 Trip Data Store · D2 Sensor Window Buffer · D3 Evidence Storage     &lt;b&gt;External Entities:&lt;/b&gt; Rider · Sensors (Accelerometer &amp; Gyroscope) · GPS System · Camera&#xa;&lt;b&gt;Note:&lt;/b&gt; GPS Speed Data feeds 4.0 Event Validation (speed gate: &lt; 15 km/h suppresses detection). 3.2 ML Analysis activates in AI Assist mode only. D1 provides Vehicle Profile to 5.0 for fuel estimation." vertex="1">
